engineer is a shelved tamil language film directed by gandhi krishna and written by sujatha originally slated to be released in 1999 . the film was based on the true story of the sardar &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; dam project and was being made in tamil with planned versions in telugu and hindi too . the film had featured arvind swamy and madhuri dixit in the leading roles , with music composed by a.r. rahman and cinematography by jeeva . however , the film was shelved after 80 percent of shooting was completed . despite reports in 2004 with a new look with a different cast and producer , this has proved to be &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; .